## 🔹 1. What is REST API

REST = Representational State Transfer

Simple meaning:

> REST API = API that uses HTTP methods to send and receive data

REST APIs use:

* URL
* HTTP method
* Headers
* Body
* Response

Example:

```text
GET /api/devices
POST /api/login
GET /api/features
POST /api/connect
```

These are REST APIs.

