## 🔹 5. REST API returns JSON

Most healthcare tools use JSON.

Example:

```json
{
  "deviceId": "123",
  "status": "connected"
}
```

Example role response:

```json
{
  "role": "FSE",
  "features": ["enumerator", "connect", "logs"]
}
```

QA must check JSON.

