## 🔹 7. Real QA Scenario (HPM)

Test login API

```text
POST /api/login
```

Check:

* Status code = 200
* Token present
* Role correct

Test role API

```text
GET /api/features
```

Check:

* FSE → full features
* User → limited features

Test device API

```text
GET /api/devices
```

Check:

* Device list correct
* Status correct

Test connect API

```text
POST /api/connect
```

Check:

* Device connected
* Backend updated

This is real API testing.

